<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6065fb38-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006"><num value="2006">§ 2006.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary to carry out this chapter, to remain available until expended—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6065fb39-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $15,000,000 for fiscal year 2006;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6065fb3a-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $20,000,000 for fiscal year 2007;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6065fb3b-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> $30,000,000 for fiscal year 2008;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6065fb3c-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> $40,000,000 for fiscal year 2009; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id6065fb3d-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s2006/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> $50,000,000 for fiscal year 2010.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id6065fb3e-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/193/s7">Pub. L. 106–193, § 7</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tIX/s968/a">Pub. L. 109–58, title IX, § 968(a)</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/898">119 Stat. 898</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
