<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id6065fb41-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/106/193/s7">section 7 of Pub. L. 106–193</ref> was set out in a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t30/s1902">section 1902 of this title</ref> prior to the general amendment of <ref href="/us/pl/106/193">Pub. L. 106–193</ref> by <ref href="/us/pl/109/58">Pub. L. 109–58</ref>.</p>
</note>
